---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { SITE } from '../lib/site';

const lastUpdated = '2026-04-24';
---
<Base title={`Terms of Use — ${SITE.name}`} description="Terms governing use of the Mountville Motors website.">
  <section class="hero-legal">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Terms of Use</p>
      <h1>The fine print, in plain English.</h1>
      <p class="lede">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section legal">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="intro">
        These terms govern your use of <strong>mountvillemotors.com</strong> and related properties operated by
        {SITE.legalName} ("we," "us," "our"). By using the site, you agree to these terms. If you don't agree, please
        don't use the site.
      </p>

      <h2>Site purpose</h2>
      <p>
        This website provides information about our dealership, vehicles, financing process, and a way to contact us
        or apply for financing. It is informational and does not constitute an offer of credit, a guarantee of
        approval, or a binding sales agreement. Specific vehicle pricing, financing terms, and approval are determined
        in person at the dealership and subject to verification.
      </p>

      <h2>Inventory and pricing</h2>
      <p>
        Vehicle availability, pricing, and specifications can change without notice. We make every effort to keep
        listings current, but errors happen. Final terms are what's agreed to in writing at the time of sale.
        Photos and descriptions are representative; come see the actual vehicle before committing.
      </p>

      <h2>Financing</h2>
      <p>
        We offer in-house ("buy here, pay here") financing. Approval is based on income verification, identity,
        residence, and other factors at our discretion. Down payment ranges and weekly payment ranges shown on this
        site are typical examples — your specific terms will be presented in writing for your review and signature
        before any agreement.
      </p>

      <h2>Text messages (TCPA)</h2>
      <p>
        By providing your phone number on any form or texting us first, you consent to receive text messages from
        {SITE.legalName} regarding your inquiry, appointments, financing, payments, and related communications.
        Message and data rates may apply. Reply <strong>STOP</strong> to opt out at any time. Reply <strong>HELP</strong>
        for help. Consent is not a condition of purchase.
      </p>

      <h2>Disclaimer of warranties</h2>
      <p>
        The website is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, express or implied. We don't guarantee the
        site will be error-free, uninterrupted, or always up to date. Any reliance you place on website information
        is at your own risk.
      </p>
      <p>
        Vehicle warranties, where applicable, are governed by the specific terms in your purchase agreement and
        applicable state and federal law. Used vehicles are sold subject to inspection and any disclosed conditions —
        ask for details on each specific vehicle.
      </p>

      <h2>Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the fullest extent permitted by law, {SITE.legalName} is not liable for indirect, incidental, special,
        or consequential damages arising from your use of the site or any third-party services linked from it.
      </p>

      <h2>External links</h2>
      <p>
        Our site may link to third-party websites (e.g., Google Maps, our review platform). We are not responsible
        for the content, privacy practices, or terms of those external sites.
      </p>

      <h2>Intellectual property</h2>
      <p>
        Site content, layout, and trademarks are the property of {SITE.legalName} or our licensors. You may not
        reproduce, modify, or commercially use the content without permission.
      </p>

      <h2>Governing law</h2>
      <p>
        These terms are governed by the laws of the Commonwealth of Pennsylvania, without regard to conflict-of-law
        principles. Any dispute will be resolved in the appropriate state or federal courts located in Lancaster County,
        Pennsylvania.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to these terms</h2>
      <p>
        We may revise these terms periodically. Continued use of the site after revisions constitutes acceptance of
        the updated terms. The "Last updated" date reflects the most recent change.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about these terms?</p>
      <ul class="contact-list">
        <li><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href={`tel:${SITE.phoneTel}`}>{SITE.phone}</a></li>
        <li><strong>Mail:</strong> {SITE.address.full}</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="footer-note">
        These terms are provided as a starting framework. {SITE.legalName} reserves the right to amend as needed for
        legal compliance and operational changes. For specific legal questions, consult an attorney.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .hero-legal { background: var(--c-navy); color: var(--c-silver-l); padding: var(--space-2xl) 0; }
  .hero-legal h1 { color: var(--c-white); }
  .hero-legal .eyebrow { color: var(--c-amber); border-color: var(--c-amber); }
  .hero-legal .lede { color: var(--c-silver); font-size: 14px; }

  .legal { background: var(--c-white); }
  .legal .intro { font-size: 17px; color: var(--c-charcoal-70); margin-bottom: var(--space-xl); }
  .legal h2 { color: var(--c-navy); margin-top: var(--space-xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-md); font-size: 22px; }
  .legal p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--c-charcoal); }
  .legal ul { padding-left: 22px; }
  .legal li { padding: 4px 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--c-charcoal); }
  .contact-list { list-style: none; padding-left: 0; margin-top: var(--space-md); }
  .contact-list li { padding: 6px 0; }
  .footer-note { font-size: 13px; color: var(--c-charcoal-70); font-style: italic; margin-top: var(--space-xl); padding-top: var(--space-md); border-top: 1px solid var(--c-line); }
</style>
